metadata.description:
The Journey of Click Mint Pass Exposure 003 by @geekiebunny

The camera case signed and decorated by the winners of the auctions so far, surrounded by all the shots that I took & considered for the mint of Exposure 003. 

I ultimately selected the shot above the camera case. 
For the full story of why the shot of the spiral staircase was my choice: https://twitter.com/geekiebunny/status/1589179233985007616

This is an airdrop for  
- all the bidders of the auction for @GuyNorcal's Click Mint Pass Exposure 003,  
- GuyNorcal  
- Exposure 002's LostinInfinity 
as a token of my heartfelt appreciation.
